<lb n="1015b11" ed="T"/><anchor type="circle"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_1015005" n="1015005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_1015005" n="1015005"/>乃至四者謂梵世愛未盡。於淨四靜慮。或
